== 地位 ==
現在《歡樂頌》是[[歐洲聯盟盟歌|歐盟盟歌]]，已被寫入《[[歐盟憲法|歐盟憲法]]》。[[歐盟之父|歐盟之父]][[理查德·尼古拉斯·冯·康登霍维-凯勒奇|理查德·尼古拉斯·冯·康登霍维-凯勒奇]]建議《歡樂頌》作為歐盟盟歌<ref>{{Cite web|title=Exchange of letters between Richard Coudenhove-Kalergi and Paul M. G. Lévy (3 August 1955 to 5 September 1955)|url=https://www.cvce.eu/en/obj/exchange_of_letters_between_richard_coudenhove_kalergi_and_paul_m_g_levy_3_august_1955_to_5_september_1955-en-34a3b196-9a23-4e9e-a977-94e31495b169.html|access-date=2022-03-03|date=2012-09-14|work=CVCE.EU by UNI.LU|language=en}}</ref>。

